text: Kerry Knowler (born 26 August 1967 in Sydney) is an Australian rower. She competed in the women's quadruple sculls event at the 2000 Summer Olympics in Sydney. ==References== Category:Australian female rowers Category:Rowers at the 2000 Summer Olympics Category:Rowers from Sydney Category:Olympic rowers of Australia Category:1967 births Category:Living people
